title: Code Name: Tiranga
subTitle: An undercover agent is on a mission to avenge the terrorist attacks committed on Indian soil in 2001. Eventually, the mission leads her to a point of no return.

title: The Last Color
subTitle: Choti, a young tightrope walker, wishes to pursue her education but struggles to make a living. She soon befriends Noor, a widow who yearns to play Holi but is forced to live a life of abstinence.

title: Chakravyuh
subTitle: Kabir infiltrates a Maoist organisation to help Adil Khan, who is a decorated police officer and his friend. As he gets deeper into the organisation, Kabir starts sympathising with the group's plight and starts having second thoughts.

title: CityLights
subTitle: Deepak Singh, an ex-army person from Rajasthan, moves to Mumbai with his family hoping for a better lifestyle. However, upon arrival, he realises that everything is not as easy as it seems.

title: State of Siege: Temple Attack
subTitle: Armed with state-of-the-art equipment and a brilliant plan, National Security Guard commandos risk their lives to save innocent people caught in a terrorist attack on a temple in Gujarat.

title: Poorna
subTitle: Poorna Malavath, a 13-year-old girl from Telangana, becomes the youngest female in history to climb and reach the summit of Mount Everest.

title: Zero
subTitle: A vertically-challenged bachelor with a larger-than-life personality discovers his life's purpose through his relationships with two wildly different women.

title: The Kashmir Files
subTitle: A young college student sets out to uncover the truth behind his parents' brutal killings in Kashmir, leading him to a web of lies and conspiracies.

title: Badla
subTitle: Naina, a successful entrepreneur, gets caught in a web of accusations when her lover is found dead. Later, she hires a reputable lawyer to work with her on the case.

title: Goodbye
subTitle: A family crumbles when the mother suddenly passes away and the children try to rush home to complete her final rites. However, differing opinions cause clashes among the clan.

title: Mission Raniganj: The Great Bharat Rescue
subTitle: Jaswant Singh Gill, a mining engineer, leads a challenging rescue mission to save 65 miners trapped in a flooded coal mine.

title: Aligarh
subTitle: Ramchandra Siras, a professor on whom a sting operation is carried out to determine his sexual orientation, forms a special bond with the journalist who covers his story.

title: Aligarh
subTitle: Ramchandra Siras, a professor on whom a sting operation is carried out to determine his sexual orientation, forms a special bond with the journalist who covers his story.

title: Sherdil: The Pilibhit Saga
subTitle: A sacrificed village leader, Gangaram, embarks on a journey in search of a dangerous tiger that threatens people.

title: Sniff
subTitle: Sunny, who lacks the sense of smell, finds his olfactory abilities enhanced after becoming a victim of a laboratory accident, which turns him into a superhero.

title: Jail
subTitle: A false drug accusation by a friend destroys Parag's life. He struggles through prison, clinging to hope for legal assistance to prove his innocence.

title: Footfairy
subTitle: A CBI officer investigates a string of gruesome murders committed by a serial killer with a foot festish. However, things take an ugly turn when he gets close to catching the killer.

title: Karthik Calling Karthik
subTitle: Karthik leads a taxing life as a scorned office worker until his own voice offers him the key to love and prosperity over a series of early morning phone calls.

title: Firaaq
subTitle: In the aftermath of Gujarat's violent 2002 riots, victims find their lives changed forever and reel from the deep impact the upheaval left on them.

title: Bareilly Ki Barfi
subTitle: In the small-town of Bareilly, a free-spirited Bitti hates that she is being pressured into getting married. But when she reads a book that reflects her life, she sets out to find its author.

title: Gully Boy
subTitle: The life of an underdog rapper from Dharavi who struggles to express his views on social issues through rapping, changes completely after he bumps into Shrikant alias MC Sher.

title: Swatantra Veer Savarkar
subTitle: After witnessing the tyranny of Britishers at a very young age, Vinayak Damodar Savarkar joins the struggle for India's freedom and faces severe incidents in his life.

title: Mr. & Mrs. Mahi
subTitle: Former cricketer Mahendra marries Mahima, a doctor with a passion for cricket. However, upon discovering her exceptional skills, he encourages her to pursue a professional career in the sport.

title: Agent Vinod
subTitle: On a mission to decipher a colleague's dying message, RAW agent Vinod travels across different countries and uncovers a dangerous conspiracy against India.

title: Agent Vinod
subTitle: On a mission to decipher a colleague's dying message, RAW agent Vinod travels across different countries and uncovers a dangerous conspiracy against India.

title: Dhaakad
subTitle: Despite her reservations, Agent Agni takes up the mission to track and capture Rudraveer, a trafficker in India. However, the assignment soon takes her down unnavigated routes.

title: Saheb, Biwi Aur Gangster 3
subTitle: Madhvi Devi relishes her political power but worries about losing it upon her husband Aditya's release from prison. To prevent this, she recruits Uday, a gangster, to assassinate him.

title: Sonchiriya
subTitle: After their leader's death, a group of dacoits splits up and runs away. On the way, they meet two women and help them escape their family and reach the hospital.

title: Vicky Donor
subTitle: Vicky, a lively young man, works as a sperm donor for Dr Baldev Chaddha and proves to be highly successful. Consequently, Baldev's clinic thrives with the help of Vicky's contributions.

title: Attack
subTitle: A terrorist attack renders Arjun paralysed and traumatised with thoughts of his dead lover. When the attacker returns, Arjun put his life on the line to serve his nation and seek revenge.

title: Raanjhanaa
subTitle: A carefree youngster sacrifices his love after his childhood sweetheart plans to marry a man from her own community. Nevertheless, fate convinces him to pursue his lady love at any cost.

title: Judgementall Hai Kya
subTitle: Bobby, a dubbing artist who is haunted by a childhood trauma, rents out a portion of her house to Keshav and Rima. However, she repeatedly stalks the young couple and is suspicious of Keshav.

title: Jawaani Jaaneman
subTitle: Jazz, a 40-year-old man, leads a frivolous casanova lifestyle in London. However, when Tia, a young woman claiming to be his daughter, enters his life, he decides to mend his ways.

title: Ground Zero
subTitle: Following the brutal attack on Parliament in 2001, armed police officer Dubey takes the lead in an investigation against Ghazi Baba.
